text: KLBG may refer to: * KLBG-LP (92.5 FM), a defunct radio station in Glide, Oregon, United States * KJMJ (580 AM), a radio station in Alexandria, Louisiana, United States which held the call sign KLBG from 1995 to 2000 * Kalaburagi railway station, a railway station in the Kalaburagi district of the Indian state of Karnataka, with the station code KLBG
title: KLBG
